quran[21]{c,v,t,f}:
  51,52,"Báyẹn ni (ọ̀rọ̀ ṣe rí)! Òjíṣẹ́ kan kò wá bá àwọn tó ṣíwájú wọn àfi kí wọ́n wí pé: “Òpìdán tàbí wèrè ni.”"
  51,53,"Ṣé wọn sọ àsọọ́lẹ̀ nípa rẹ̀ láààrin ara wọn ni? Rárá o! Ìjọ olùtayọ-ẹnu-ààlà ni wọ́n ni."
  51,54,"Nítorí náà, ṣẹ́rí kúrò lọ́dọ̀ wọn ná. Ìwọ kì í ṣe ẹni tí A máa bá wí."
  52,43,"Tàbí wọ́n ní ọlọ́hun kan lẹ́yìn Allāhu ni? Mímọ́ ni fún Allāhu tayọ n̄ǹkan tí wọ́n ń fi ṣẹbọ sí I."
  52,44,"Tí wọ́n bá rí apá kan nínú sánmọ̀ tó ya lúlẹ̀, wọ́n á wí pé: “Ẹ̀ṣújò rẹgẹdẹ ni (wọn kò níí gbàgbọ́).”"
  52,45,"Nítorí náà, fi wọ́n sílẹ̀ títí wọn yóò fi bá ọjọ́ wọn tí wọn máa pa wọ́n sínú rẹ̀ pàdé."
  53,37,"àti (tírà Ànábì) ’Ibrọ̄hīm, ẹni tó mú (òfin Allāhu) ṣẹ,"
  53,38,"pé dájúdájú ẹlẹ́rù-ẹ̀ṣẹ̀ kan kò níí ru ẹrù-ẹ̀ṣẹ̀ ẹlòmíìràn.{1}.",1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah an-Nahl; 16:25.]
  53,39,"Àti pé kò sí kiní kan fún ènìyàn àfi ohun tó ṣe níṣẹ́."
  54,28,"Kí o sì fún wọn ní ìró pé dájúdájú pípín ni omi láààrin wọn. Gbogbo ìpín omi sì wà fún ẹni tí ó bá kàn láti wá sí odò."
  54,29,"Wọ́n pe ẹni wọn. Ó yọ́ kẹ́lẹ́kẹ́lẹ́ nawọ́ mú (ràkúnmí náà mọ́lẹ̀). Ó sì pa á."
  54,30,"Báwo ni ìyà Mi àti ìkìlọ̀ Mi ti rí ná (lára wọn)?"
  55,22,"Òkúta oníyebíye àti ìlẹ̀kẹ̀ iyùn ń jáde nínú àwọn (odò) méjèèjì náà."
  55,23,"Nítorí náà, èwo nínú àwọn ìdẹ̀ra Olúwa ẹ̀yin ènìyàn àti àlùjànnú ni ẹ máa pè ní irọ́?"
  55,24,"Ti (Allāhu) ni àwọn ọkọ̀ ojú-omi gogoro tó ń rìn nínú agbami òdò (tí wọ́n dà) bí àpáta gíga."
  56,13,"Wọ́n pọ̀ nínú àwọn ẹni àkọ́kọ́."
  56,14,"Wọ́n sì kéré nínú àwọn ẹni Ìkẹ́yìn."
  56,15,"(Wọn yóò wà) lórí ìtẹ́ tí wọ́n fi góòlù hun."
  57,4,"Òun ni Ẹni tí Ó ṣẹ̀dá àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ilẹ̀ fún ọjọ́ mẹ́fà. Lẹ́yìn náà, Ó gúnwà sí orí Ìtẹ́-ọlá. Ó mọ n̄ǹkan tó ń wọ inú ilẹ̀ àti n̄ǹkan tó ń jáde láti inú rẹ̀, àti n̄ǹkan tó ń sọ̀kalẹ̀ láti inú sánmọ̀ àti n̄ǹkan tó ń gùnkè sínú rẹ̀. Àti pé Ó wà pẹ̀lú yín ní ibikíbi tí ẹ bá wà (pẹ̀lú ìmọ̀ Rẹ̀).{1} Allāhu sì ni Olùríran nípa ohun tí ẹ̀ ń ṣe níṣẹ́..",1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al-Mujādilah 58:7.]
  57,5,"TiRẹ̀ ni ìjọba àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ilẹ̀. Ọ̀dọ̀ Allāhu sì ni wọ́n máa ṣẹ́rí àwọn ọ̀rọ̀ ẹ̀dá padà sí."
  57,6,"Ó ń ti òru bọ inú ọ̀sán. Ó sì ń ti ọ̀sán bọ inú òru. Òun sì ni Onímọ̀ nípa ohun tó wà nínú igbá-àyà ẹ̀dá."